. &amp; W. train with Engine No. 68 with two railroad men in front. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_832ff95c5ce71f890231d5f6d3aa5383" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_cbd411fa425bad56f807b77d984e21de" level="item"><did><unittitle>Engine with "Pittston" and L.V.R. on the front. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_205b2fc1cdb0f67007c8d37062dcf92d" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_de17f9a4ef4e208f9481f6433f1c7e93" level="item"><did><unittitle>Engine with four men in front and one in the engine. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_4d8024d9c67a858771c0baece983f185" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01></dsc>
